{"tid":1307489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國主持人以幽默評中國社會信用系統","createTime":"2019-07-11T14:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T16:08:40.000Z","uid":36073,"like":83,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"30382b247185f9499d22be774c708bf43bc68bbc","tid":1307489,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"各位，呢排傷心咗咁耐，俾啲笑料你哋嘆<br />\n<br />\n美國主持人 Stephen Colbert 原來早喺一年前已經提到中國社會信用系統，所有荒謬之處。<br />\n唔太識英文嘅都可以睇咗先，去片：<br />\n<br />\nEveryone In China Is Getting A &ldquo;Social Credit Score&rdquo; - The Late Late Show with Stephen Colbert<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/colbertlateshow/videos/1397174723760608?s=1488910054&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcolbertlateshow%2Fvideos%2F1397174723760608%3Fs%3D1488910054%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjryOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=a41ea7ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/colbertlateshow/videos/1397174723760608?s=1488910054&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\nStephen Colbert 主要提到，中國社會信用系統嘅特徵：<br />\n－每人一開始給予1000分，例如違例泊車 -5分、英勇行為 +30分<br />\n－很多行為都會引致扣分，如亂過馬路、車廂內吸煙、買太多電子遊戲 等<br />\n－當你亂過馬路，閉路電視會拍下證據作公審<br />\n－國家聲稱以信用系統作「淨化社會」<br />\n<br />\n但他就這些特徵諷刺：<br />\n－人們可以編造「英勇行為」，自己放火自己救<br />\n－就如你玩過滑浪飛船後的驚喊相被「公審」一樣<br />\n－ 中國應先「淨化」自己的空氣<br />\n<br />\n主持更介紹團隊的一位編劇 James 是「中國人」，但 James 辯稱他是台灣人。最後 Stephen 鬧他，「這節目要維持『一中政策』，現在你弄得我們也要被『淨化』了。」"},{"pid":"80f01a6c3216412b71f5302d0a22749831cb695d","tid":1307489,"uid":258370,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:00:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"958be6072e428b56279504ba66fa9a56264fbec2","tid":1307489,"uid":94075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:07:04.000Z","msg":"唔太笑得出 有都係苦笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70dcfbb4d0704ca3bab1aa7599ada639012d8537","tid":1307489,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:07:08.000Z","msg":"其實段片好耐之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed73baec124e51110e856ff2b0f391f6f051d46","tid":1307489,"uid":36432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:07:51.000Z","msg":"John Oliver笑習大大嗰集都有提過"},{"pid":"71ac8c97ac2407734d84d4f787b7c1fd905c4c67","tid":1307489,"uid":36073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:08:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n主持更介紹團隊的一位編劇 James 是「中國人」，但 James 辯稱他是台灣人。最後 Stephen 鬧他，「這節目要維持『一中政策』，現在你弄得我們也要被『淨化』了。」</blockquote>呢單嘢值得煲大佢<br />\n等全世界都笑鳩中共嘅制度<br />\n再加多少少 解釋<br />\n話 如果冇真普選 <br />\n香港都就快變成咁樣</blockquote><br />\n所以我哋嘅自由唔係必然<br />\n比送中更可怕嘅係，信用系統完完全全剝奪人權，社會都會因為評分而造成<span style=\"color: red;\">極端階級化</span>"},{"pid":"ccd9589f991015364cc65884ed91d948a924056c","tid":1307489,"uid":68483,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:11:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6F51dw4d1CM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6F51dw4d1CM&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjryOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=d8f68b36\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6F51dw4d1CM</a><br />\n有字幕版"},{"pid":"83ad86b5d89866ab5cd789e4c87bb083445af4ff","tid":1307489,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"各位可以隨便 share ，喚起關注"},{"pid":"3c97d5fbb825c15550a534eb547eda63ca2fa9dc","tid":1307489,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac90e34695512723b16d9f6e4acbea6b200b68e","tid":1307489,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:16:12.000Z","msg